Ingredients:
- A tub of cream cheese
- Imitation crab, chopped (if you have real crab then go nuts!)
- Shrimp, chopped (optional)
- Hot sauce of choice (I like Sriracha)
- Japanese mayo
- Garlic powder
- Onion powder
- Chili powder
- Green onions, chopped
- White onion, diced
- Lemon (optional)
- Vessel of choice (I like wafer crackers! Salted potato chips are good too :)

Directions:
1. Prepare the imitation and crab by chopping into small pieces
2. In a tub, combine all listed ingredient
3. Enjoy with your crackers or chips!
